    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Cosella ceratopudenda Flechtmann, n. sp. AD, anterior dorsal aspect; CD, caudal dorsal aspect; CGF, coxigenital area of female, with detail of coxal pointed granules; E, empodium (enlarged); GF, genitalia of female, sp spinelike projection on genitalia rim; GM, genitalia of male; L, lateral aspect of female; L 1, leg I; L 2, leg II." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155885/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.155886>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Cosella ceratopudenda Flechtmann, n. sp. L­AD, anterior dorsal aspect of larva; L­V, ventral aspect of larval \" genital \" area; PN­AD, anterior dorsal aspect of protonymph; PN­V, ventral aspect of nymphal \" genital \" area." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/155886/files/figure.png" ;
